episodes.overview: Sharon sets her plan into motion, Dev arranges a summit meeting with Corey's father, and Chesney acts as peacemaker for Fiz and Tyrone

episodes.name: Monday, 26th April 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Sharon steals from Gail as pressure mounts. Dev drives Asha further towards Corey. George disapproves of Todd's business methods

episodes.name: Wednesday, 28th April 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Sharon helps Sarah to throw Sam a birthday party. Asha enjoys living with Corey. Carla and Peter take advantage of an empty house

episodes.name: Wednesday, 28th April 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Sam takes Sharon into his confidence. Peter receives great news about his transplant. Kevin and Abi are shocked at Tyrone's presumption

episodes.name: Friday, 30th April 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Sharon gives Sam a message to pass to Nick. Eileen berates George for dismissing Todd. Simon breaks cover to visit his dad

episodes.name: Friday, 30th April 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Peter gets caught in the crossfire of Simon's escape. Todd receives a poignant reminder of his past. Tyrone accuses Kevin and Abi of snubbing Alina

episodes.name: Monday, 3rd May 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Nick and Leanne think they're safe in their hideout but Sharon will go to any lengths to get Harvey's heavies their address.

episodes.name: Monday, 3rd May 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: After Kevin and Tyrone's row, Abi's worried about her wedding then more setbacks leave her certain her big day is doomed.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 5th May 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: As Nina and Seb walk along the canal they encounter a gang. Kelly slaps Nina, which prompts Corey and the gang to attack.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 5th May 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: With Nina and Seb suffering horrific injuries, Kelly and Corey try to convince everyone they know nothing about the attack.

episodes.name: Friday, 7th May 2021 #10319
episodes.overview: Corey tells uneasy Asha he wasn't involved in the attack but asks her to provide him with a false alibi. Will she lie for him?

episodes.name: Friday, 7th May 2021 #10320
episodes.overview: As Abi waits for news on Seb, she tries to stay positive. Meanwhile, Nina is struggling to remember what happened.

episodes.name: Monday, 10th May 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview:
Corey pretends he's watched Tenet, and tries to coerce Asha into giving him an alibi. Amy warns Asha against lying to the police, and claiming that she watched Christopher Nolan's latest flick.

Fiz decides Seb's passing is the perfect moment to continue bad-mouthing Tyrone, and then wonders why the poor bloke left her in the first place.

Abi channels her inner Poirot and demands that Nina tells her who murdered her son Sebastian.

episodes.name: Monday, 10th May 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview:
Corey enlists his Dad to help convince the police that he watched Tenet.

Fiz apologises to Tyrone for being an insensitive prick.

Abi rants at the screenwriters for letting Corey and Kelly off the hook with the murder of her son.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 12th May 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Abi tells Kevin she won't rest until Seb's attacker is caught, while Summer confides in Paul about the night of the assault.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 12th May 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Kelly faces some tough questioning - will she tell the police what really happened? Imran sits in on the interview.

episodes.name: Friday, 14th May 2021
episodes.overview: Summer doesn't turn up for school. Abi's anger mounts when she learns Nina's appearance may have triggered the attack. Laura warns Toyah and Imran that she wants Kelly to live with her. Ronnie's determined to make amends with Ed.

episodes.name: Monday, 17th May 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Jenny goes for a ride in Ed's done-up camper van with Ronnie -will the pair act on their sizzling chemistry?

episodes.name: Monday, 17th May 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Gail makes a discovery as she's minding Sam. Asha tells Aadi that she has a plan to get the truth out of Corey.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 19th May 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Jenny makes it clear to Ronnie that it's time to move out of the B&B but is distraught. Will she explain why to Daisy?

episodes.name: Wednesday, 19th May 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Sharon wangles her way into Dev's place, where she sends a message to Simon from Aadi's console. Will he take the bait?

episodes.name: Friday, 21st May 2021
episodes.overview: Sharon tips off Harvey's heavies who snatch Sam. A panicked Natasha calls the police, how far will Harvey go? Jenny squirms when Fiz confides her pain over Tyrone's affair. Later, Fiz learns that Ty and Alina want to buy a flat.

episodes.name: Monday, 24th May 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Tyrone begins to feel the pinch as he forks out for shoes for the girls and some bits and bobs Alina wants for the flat!

episodes.name: Monday, 24th May 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Despite Leanne's fears, Nick returns home to search for Sam where he's then cornered by one of Harvey's dodgy thugs...

episodes.name: Wednesday, 26th May 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Realising Sam's ordeal wasn't an accident, Nick tells Leanne he can't return to the hideout while his son's still in danger.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 26th May 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: With Elaine having fallen out with Cathy, Tim invites his mum to move into No. 4. But how will Sally take the news?

episodes.name: Friday, 28th May 2021
episodes.overview: Suspicious Jenny learns of the link between Harvey and Sharon! Daniel and Adam offer to be liver donors for Peter. Nina's devastated to realise that Abi doesn't want her at Seb's funeral, while Asha pursues Corey for a confession.

episodes.name: Monday, 31st May 2021
episodes.overview: As Jenny twigs Sharon was involved in Sam's kidnap, she's in grave danger... Asha tells Corey she wants to get back together. Rita finds Sharon about to do a runner and demands answers. Abi wants Nina to wear one of her goth dresses to Seb's funeral.

episodes.name: Tuesday, 1st June 2021
episodes.overview: Linda confides her pregnancy secret in Sharon and is relieved when a doctor at the hospital informs her that the baby is fine. Jean convinces Mo there's nothing to worry about, then she and Kat throw her a leaving do as she sets off for a cruise!

episodes.name: Thursday, 3rd June 2021
episodes.overview: Asha begs Abi not to attack Corey, insisting that her son Seb wouldn't have wanted his mum back in prison. Will Abi listen? Later, Abi helps Asha pull off her dangerous plan to expose Corey's guilt for the fatal attack but will the pair succeed?

episodes.name: Friday, 4th June 2021
episodes.overview: As groggy Corey staggers around, then falls down the stairs, Abi, Asha and Nina must decide whether to call for help. Carla accuses Sarah of talking Adam out of not going through with the transplant to get back at her for sleeping with Adam.

episodes.name: Monday, 7th June 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: A compatible liver is finally found for Peter. Carla says a tearful goodbye as he gets ready for surgery. Will it go well?

episodes.name: Monday, 7th June 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Johnny decides to sell the pub. Elsewhere, Fiz hits the roof when she discovers Alina has given Hope eyelash extensions!

episodes.name: Wednesday, 9th June 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: There's another incident at Alina and Tyrone's when Hope runs out in front of a car, leading Fiz to tell Ty he can't see the girls.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 9th June 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Things get fruity between Bernie and Dev during a 'pretend' date meant to prove to Aadi that his dad has still got it!

episodes.name: Friday, 11th June 2021
episodes.overview: The custody battle for Hope and Ruby is on. Tyrone accuses Fiz of trying to get him arrested to improve her chance of success. Mary overhears Dev telling Steve he copped off with Bernie because he was drunk. Grieving Nina downs a bottle of vodka...

episodes.name: Monday 14 June
episodes.overview: Nina's drinking has Roy worried sick, especially when she gets smashed with friends and then disappears in a taxi... Mary confesses to Bernie that Dev only got together with her because he was drunk, leaving Bernie to take revenge!

episodes.name: Thursday 17 June
episodes.overview: Daisy tells Abi she's worried about Nina. When Nina then gets plastered in a hotel bar and spots Corey, will Abi help? Nick, Leanne and Simon nervously return home. Will Leanne agree to give evidence against drug lord Harvey in court?

episodes.name: Sunday, 20th June 2021
episodes.overview: Nick and Sam's first Father's Day together proves eventful. Summer gives Billy and Todd cause for concern. Gemma feels pressured into a decision.

episodes.name: Monday, 21st June 2021
episodes.overview: Sharon begs Rita for help to make a new life. Nick suggests Natasha and Sam move back to London. Summer is diagnosed with diabetes. Sean helps struggling Carol. Tracy advises Emma to play hard to get with Curtis.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 23rd June 2021
episodes.overview: Leanne and Sharon take the stand in court. Sean has a wake-up call about Double Glammy. Curtis is left confused as Emma plays it cool. Billy asks a thrilled Todd to move in. Tyrone fails his motorbike test.

episodes.name: Friday, 25th June 2021
episodes.overview: Tyrone turns to Fiz when he discovers Kirsty has died. Rita offers Sharon cash to start afresh. Sean asks Daniel to help expose Double Glammy. Daisy sets her heart on buying the Rovers. Emma fears she's missed her chance.

episodes.name: Tuesday, 29th June 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Alina makes an upsetting discovery about Tyrone's past. Daisy exercises her authority in order to punish Sean. James receives some positive career news.

episodes.name: Tuesday, 29th June 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Alina's baby bombshell throws Tyrone into turmoil. Jenny puts Daisy firmly in her place. James asks Danny to revive their relationship.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 30th June 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: David pesters Gail to allow Nick to see Sam. James attracts some unwanted online attention prior to a press conference. Fiz offers to support Tyrone.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 30th June 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Family feuding causes heartache for Gail. James bravely goes public with his sexuality. Tyrone avoids telling Fiz of Alina's pregnancy.

episodes.name: Friday, 2nd July 2021
episodes.overview: Fiz learns that Tyrone and Alina are expecting. Sarah eyes Nick's half-share of Underworld. Billy frets when Summer refuses to face reality.

episodes.name: Monday, 5th July 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Todd decides to propose to Billy but then Summer hands Todd a threatening anonymous letter she found on the porch, and that throws everything into question.

episodes.name: Monday, 5th July 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Sarah video calls Izzy and sees a man in the background -who is the stranger? Fiz tells Tyrone that he has to tell the girls about the baby today and if he doesn't, she will.

episodes.name: Tuesday, 6th July 2021
episodes.overview: Todd blames Paul for the threat made against him. Alya suspects Daisy of going after her man. Leanne appeals to Natasha on Nick's behalf.

episodes.name: Friday, 9th July 2021
episodes.overview: Will unnerves Todd by introducing himself to Summer. Daisy makes her move on Ryan. Sean and George team up to win over Eileen.

episodes.name: Monday, 12th July 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Back in the dating game after Tyrone's betrayal, Fiz meets a date, Chris, in the Bistro. However, the dolled-up single mum is confronted by someone she's not expecting!

episodes.name: Monday, 12th July 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: After waking up in Daisy's bed, Ryan begs Daisy to keep it secret from his girlfriend Alya. But Daisy relishes the chance to let her know where Ryan spent the night.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 14th July 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: When Will nicks Todd's engagement ring, Todd is forced to help him steal a £7,000 heat pump. Later, as Ed reports the pump as stolen, Craig blames Paul for the theft...

episodes.name: Wednesday, 14th July 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: By playing to Steve's ego, Curtis and Emma convince him to pose for the charity calendar. Dev and Kevin are on board, too. Will Fiz take up Chris' offer to do the article?

episodes.name: Friday, 16th July 2021
episodes.overview: When Will nicks Todd's engagement ring, Todd is forced to help him steal a £7,000 heat pump. Later, as Ed reports the pump as stolen, Craig blames Paul for the theft... By playing to Steve's ego, Curtis and Emma convince him to pose for the charity calendar. Dev and Kevin are on board, too. Will Fiz take up Chris' offer to do the article?

episodes.name: Monday, 19th July 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Curtis is still trying to hide his health concerns from Emma and tries to end things to protect her. But her dad Steve thinks Curtis is cheating and confronts him.

episodes.name: Monday, 19th July 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Delighted that Sam is staying for the week, Nick allows him to decorate his room with posters but then fears that he's overstepped the mark with Leanne.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 21st July 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Curtis finally tells Emma the truth about his condition but after all the lies he's told her it seems it may be too late to save their relationship. Nick worries about Sam's health.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 21st July 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Back in the dating game, Fiz has fun with Phill in Speed Daal, but her ex Tyrone spots them and can't help feeling put out to see her enjoying herself with another man.

episodes.name: Friday, 23rd July 2021
episodes.overview: Rattled that Fiz is seeing Phill, Tyrone takes Alina to the bistro to keep an eye on Fiz's date and the more he drinks the more upset he gets. Alina feels totally humiliated. Dev wants to pull out of the charity naked calendar at the eleventh hour but is it too late? Emma worries that the stressful situation will affect Curtis' heart condition.

episodes.name: Monday, 26th July 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: James and Michael's day of fun ends in arrest. Tyrone's jealousy of Fiz's new man annoys Alina. Daniel receives a tip-off concerning Laura.

episodes.name: Monday, 26th July 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Michael urges James to lodge a complaint with the police. Toyah and Imran threaten to report Laura. Billy and Todd have a surprise for Summer.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 28th July 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Will reveals Todd's scheming to Summer and Paul. Craig learns of the Baileys' allegation against his colleague. Toyah and Imran vow to support Kelly.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 28th July 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Todd's world comes crashing down for all to see. Craig is faced with a troubling dilemma. Kelly opens up about her unhappy childhood.

episodes.name: Friday, 30th July 2021
episodes.overview: Grace is delighted to have rekindled her romance with Michael. Todd dashes to the aid of unconscious Summer. Fiz puts her family first.

episodes.name: Monday, 2nd August 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Hope feels neglected over Tyrone and Alina's pending baby. Michael and James are left disappointed and frustrated when the police refuse to take their complaint further, and Izzy is confused over an order she is working on.

episodes.name: Monday, 2nd August 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Alina is rushed to hospital after the salon flat catches fire, Craig questions PC Brody about his handling of James's arrest, and George offers Todd a place to stay.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 4th August 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Alina is horrified to think she caused the fire with one of her candles, Eileen coyly accepts George's offer of dinner, but he cancels after overhearing her chat with Mary. Billy is saddened at the thought of his cancelled wedding.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 4th August 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Evelyn suggests to a shocked Fiz that Hope might know more about the fire than she's letting on. Eileen lambasts George for cancelling their date. Izzy opens up to Carla and Sarah about the problems she's suffered during the pandemic.

episodes.name: Friday, 6th August 2021
episodes.overview: Fiz tells Hope they need to talk about the fire, Aadi's love life causes confusion, and Nina crumbles at the thought of having to relive her terrible ordeal. Meanwhile, Shona turns amateur traffic warden, dispensing home-made parking tickets.

episodes.name: Monday, 9th August 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: A panicked Shona confesses she hit 'something' while driving David's car but drove off. Later, they discover she hit Todd and that he's injured in hospital!

episodes.name: Monday, 9th August 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Having retrieved Alina's keys from arsonist Hope, Tyrone hopes that both his ex and her daughter are off the hook for the fire. But Alina has other ideas...

episodes.name: Wednesday, 11th August 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Knowing Todd's got him and Shona over a barrel, David's in even deeper trouble when he's arrested for the hit-and-run. Seb's memorial garden creates mixed reactions.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 11th August 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Already bored of their new lifestyle, Nick and Leanne put in an offer for the Bistro. But can they get Debbie to agree to their price? Alina goes looking for answers...

episodes.name: Friday, 13th August 2021
episodes.overview: It's Friday the 13th, which is definitely an unlucky day for Ty as he's finally forced to tell Alina everything. As Fiz is taken in for questioning by the police, what will she say? Someone's trashed Seb's memorial garden and a devastated Nina accuses Asha! But she's in for a shock when the true culprit is revealed... Ryan heads off to a gig.

episodes.name: Monday, 16th August 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Tyrone tells the police that Hope started the fire. Nick and Leanne get the better of Debbie.

episodes.name: Monday, 16th August 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Ryan humiliates Daisy in front of Daniel. Sally is riled by chaotic parking. Abi decides to write a victim impact statement.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 18 August 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Tyrone accidentally proposes to Alina. Adam is chuffed when Sarah considers having a baby.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 18th August 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Daisy offers to help when Bertie has a health scare. Debbie and Leanne make a formidable team.

episodes.name: Friday, 20th August 2021
episodes.overview: Tyrone bursts into tears on Fiz. Sally campaigns to have residentparking permits. Stressed-out Imran snaps at Leanne. Alya learns the truth about Ryan's 'fling'. Michael is honest with Ronnie about Grace.

episodes.name: Monday, 23rd August 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Maria is horrified when her son Liam starts struggling to breathe. The lad is rushed to hospital, where Maria is told that air pollution could be to blame.

episodes.name: Monday, 23rd August 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Imran is shocked to learn his ex-wife Sabeen is part of Corey's defence team! Tyrone gets Alina an engagement ring -but does he still have feelings for Fiz?

episodes.name: Wednesday, 25th August 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Abi fears the trial of Seb's accused attackers could be jeopardised after Corey's identity is leaked online. But Imran is still determined to win -one way or another.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 25th August 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Aggie and Ed return and are startled to find Grace packing her bags after breaking up with Michael. But Aggie refuses to let Grace leave with their granddaughter Glory.

episodes.name: Friday, 27th August 2021
episodes.overview: As the trial gets underway, Simon hassles Nina in the cafe and begs her to remember what really happened the night of the attack. Furious Roy sends Simon packing. While cleaning out the storeroom at the funeral parlour, Todd finds the ashes of serial killer Pat Phelan! Is Eileen about to get an unpleasant reminder of her evil ex-husband?

episodes.name: Monday, 30th August 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: As the trial into Seb's murder looms, Nina is triggered by a piece of music, which takes her back to the last day of her boyfriend's life, pushing her to retrace their steps.

episodes.name: Monday, 30th August 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: A series of flashback scenes show exactly what happened the night Seb and Nina were attacked in a hate crime. Meanwhile, the lawyers prepare for battle in court.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 1st September 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: At the police station, Nina signs her new statement, hoping it will ensure justice for Seb. As Nina takes to the witness box, will her recollection of the night stand up in court?

episodes.name: Wednesday, 1st September 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: After Nina's cross-examined, it's Asha's turn to take to the stand. After lawyers Sabeen and Imran question her, the upset teen takes comfort in her dad Dev's arms.

episodes.name: Friday, September 3rd 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Abi lays into Corey's dad Stefan, suggesting it's time his son started telling the truth. Inside the courtroom, Corey lies to paint himself the victim and blames Kelly.

episodes.name: Friday, 3rd September 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Fiz and Ty are devastated when Hope speaks out during her first therapy session. An ambulance is called when terminally ill Curtis collapses behind the bar at the Bistro.

episodes.name: Monday, 6th September 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Kelly tells the court it was Corey who attacked Seb. The lawyers then give their closing statements -and Abi speaks out...

episodes.name: Monday, 6th September 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: George admits to Eileen that Patsy's' ashes are actually Phelan's! Curtis does a runner on Emma on an important day.

episodes.name: Friday, 10th September 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: As the jury deliberates, Imran is still desperate to prove Kelly is innocent. Abi hunts for proof that Stefan bribed a witness.

episodes.name: Friday, 10th September 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: When the jury return their verdict, who will be found guilty of Seb's murder and taken to prison... Kelly or Corey?

episodes.name: Monday, 13th September 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Tyrone makes a desperate plea to win back his ex Fiz. Alina backtracks on her Romania trip to support guilt-ridden Ty.

episodes.name: Monday, 13th September 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Imran does the walk of shame and tells Toyah he spent the night at the office. Dev takes steps to do right by son Aadi.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 15th September 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Alina's heartbroken and exits after Tyrone tells her he wants to get back with Fiz. But Fiz tells Phill she has no interest in her ex.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 15th September 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Ken, Rita and Mary arrive at the hospital too late to say goodbye to Norris. Craig offers support to James.

episodes.name: Thursday, 16th September 2021
episodes.overview: Desperate to stop Alina from leaving, Tyrone races off to find her before she gets on a plane. Will he accept things are over? Norris' funeral arrangements start arguments. Imran goes all out to help jailed Kelly. Daniel starts his teaching placement.

episodes.name: Friday, 17th September 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: At Speed Daal, Alya is having a nightmare as the food delivery is late and a customer spots a tarantula! Zeedan saves the day.

episodes.name: Friday, 17th September 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Tyrone tries to ruin Fiz's romance with Phill. Gemma and Freda clash over Aled's op. Maria warns Gary about Sharon.

episodes.name: Monday, 20th September 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Kelly reckons her dad Rick has paid her legal fees and pales when cellmate Mia reveals a link to Rick and claims he's dead.

episodes.name: Monday, 20th September 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: After rowing with Alya, Zeedan is attacked by two thugs! Later, he admits to Yasmeen and his sister that he's in big trouble...

episodes.name: Wednesday, 22nd September 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Kelly demands the truth from Gary. Panic breaks out when Freda disappears with Aled, who's due to have his cochlear implant.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 22nd September 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Gail returns from Thailand. Zeedan tries to make amends for the damage he's done. David accuses Daniel of favouritism.

episodes.name: Friday, 24th September 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: David's beef with Daniel escalates when the tutor accuses Max of stealing his wallet and confronts the lad in the Street...

episodes.name: Friday, 24th September 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Mourners gather for Norris' funeral. Rita gives a eulogy and Billy reads a letter written by Norris, which causes mayhem!

episodes.name: Monday, 27th September 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: David reports Daniel for assaulting Max, who was accused of stealing the tutor's wallet. Shona refuses to support David.

episodes.name: Monday, 27th September 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Sabeen wants Imran to help her free Harvey Gaskell. James learns that his parents have been threatened by Grace.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 29th September 2021 (Part  1)
episodes.overview: It's Kelly's sentencing. Kev loses it when he sees Sabeen and lashes out at the barrister for getting Corey off scot-free.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 29th September 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Toyah picks up on a vibe a between Imran and Sabeen and asks if he's sleeping with his ex. Audrey's birthday is a disaster.

episodes.name: Friday, 1st October 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Kev tries to ruin Corey's career. Audrey apologises to Rita while the family stages an intervention. Upset Asha confides in Aadi.

episodes.name: Friday, 1st October 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Imran makes an admission when Toyah finds out he's been lying to her. Will he tell her the truth about the night the trial ended?

episodes.name: Monday, 4th October 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Nina wants the truth about Corey to be known. When it seems he's outmaoneuvred her, she flips and wants him dead.

episodes.name: Monday, 4th October 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Desperate for more diners at Speed Daal, Zeedan launches a special event. Can he pull a plan to outdo the Bistro?

episodes.name: Wednesday, 6th October 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Kevin searches for Abi and, when he hears she's withdrawn £2k from their joint account, he worries she's back on drugs.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 6th October 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: At Speed Daal, Alya and Yasmeen are puzzled that none of their bookings have turned up. Zeedan blames Debbie.

episodes.name: Friday, 8th October 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Kevin follows Abi's ex Tez and, after seeing him carry out a drug deal, tries to blackmail him into revealing Abi's location.

episodes.name: Friday, 8th October 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Zeedan's confronted by his father-in-law Hashim, who makes him a horrifying offer in return for staying quiet about his secret.

episodes.name: Monday, 11th October 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Kev's stunned when he wakes to find Abi is back home. When she explains what she's been up to, is she telling the whole truth?

episodes.name: Monday, 11th October 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Toyah learns she and Imran are going to be fostering a little girl. Imran confides in Adam that Sabeen's blackmailing him.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 13th October 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Imran calls an end to Sabeen's blackmail. The barrister then has to admit to Toyah that he had a one-night stand. Will he tell all?

episodes.name: Wednesday,  13th October 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Abi's forced to go along with it when Kev says he and Debbie will sort out the wedding plans. Johnny clocks Jenny on date.

episodes.name: Friday, 15th October 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: When Roy finds a notebook filled with info on Corey, Nina vows to discover who's behind the detailed detective work.

episodes.name: Friday, 15th October 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Toyah swipes Imran's phone. Sabeen informs Imran she's been accused of misconduct and that druggy Harvey's after him.

episodes.name: Monday, 18th October 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: At Debbie's House of Horrors, a generator falls into the Platts' sinkhole. Gun-toting Abi confronts Corey but the ground gives way.

episodes.name: Monday, 18th October 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: When a prison van containing Harvey Gaskell smashes into the Alahans' car who will Dev save? Harvey steals Kev's truck.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 20th October 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Trapped in a sewer with the water rising around them, Abi and Corey have a face off. But who will get hold of the gun?

episodes.name: Wednesday, 20th October 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Harvey binds and gags Leanne and fumes when she tries to flee. Jenny falls into the sinkhole and Johnny goes in after her.

episodes.name: Friday, 22nd October 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Jenny and Johnny cling to a ladder as they wait for rescue. Can David stop Shona from playing the hero? Will anyone survive?

episodes.name: Friday, 22nd October 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Will Harvey get his revenge? Nick makes a shocking discovery. Kev hears what's happened to Abi. Dev wills Aadi to wake up.

episodes.name: Monday, 25th October 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Following last week's horror, Leo tells guilty David that had he fixed the sinkhole, the disaster wouldn't have happened.

episodes.name: Monday, 25th October 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Simon is blaming himself for getting tangled up with Harvey. Dev struggles with his guilt, and tragedy strikes the Street.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 27th October 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Asha spots a man called Stu wearing a County backpack. When he says he found it in the river, Asha's sure it's Corey's.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 27th October 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Curtis laps up the flattery as Emma praises him for all he did to help those in need. The locals confront David about the sinkhole.

episodes.name: Friday, 29th October 2021
episodes.overview: Zeedan's forced to launder more money through Speed Daal but is Ryan on to him? Emma asks Steve to fund Curtis' care. Asha and Nina approach one of Stu's friends. Will the pair end up finding him? Could Stu provide proof Corey killed Seb?

episodes.name: Monday, 1st November 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Abi's words come back to haunt her, Maria learns of the council's plans to bulldoze the Red Rec and Ryan informs Alya of his concerns about Zeedan

episodes.name: Monday, 1st November 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Curtis kicks off when Emma tries to help with his revision. Corey demands the contents of his backpack from homeless Stu.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 3rd November 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Abi confesses her deeds to Kev, who asserts he still loves her and wants to marry her! Will Abi turn up to the wedding?

episodes.name: Wednesday, 3rd November 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Curtis collapses and is rushed to hospital. Later, he has a shock proposal for Emma. Maria protests against the bypass plans.

episodes.name: Friday, 5th November 2021
episodes.overview: Abi asks Gary to help her find Corey, who is trying to flee to avoid arrest... Is Seb's killer about to be caught at long last? Steve and Tracy tell Emma they want to use their savings to pay for private care for Curtis. Nick worries about Sam.

episodes.name: Monday 8th November 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: At an appeal hearing Kelly is released with immediate effect! Back on the street, is there room for her at Imran and Toyah's?

episodes.name: Monday 8th November 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: At Natasha's funeral, a silent Sam clings to Nick as his dad reads out his eulogy. Abi tells Jack she'd like to adopt him.

episodes.name: Tuesday, 9th November 2021
episodes.overview: Tyrone muscles in when Phill offers to help Hope with her homework. Nick and Leanne seek help for grieving Sam. Kelly tries to make the best of her digs and goes to great lengths to try to get Nina's forgiveness. Aadi is hurt by Dev's actions.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 10th November 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Tyrone wins an admirer and flirts with her on a play date. Aadi walks out on Dev. Leanne tries to connect with Sam.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 10th November 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Adam warns Daniel not to get involved with Daisy. Besotted babysitter Summer later clocks the dad sneaking Daisy into his flat.

episodes.name: Tuesday, 16th November 2021
episodes.overview: Kelly's forced to steal a mobile phone but her crime is exposed... She then goes on the run unaware Aadi's got Dev to let her move in. Tyrone goes on a date with Isla and is chuffed when they hit it off. But Isla's husband comes calling and punches stunned Ty.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 17th November 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Living on the streets, Kelly fails to reach Aadi. Later, at a hotel, a stranger tells Kelly she's welcome in his bedroom any time.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 17th November 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Johnny's funeral day sees Jenny drunkenly turn on Daisy. Nick's furious when Max upsets Sam. Tim visits Faye in prison.

episodes.name: Friday, 19th November 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Debbie insists jailed Ray admits to assaulting Faye or she'll report him to the police for causing Johnny's sinkhole death.

episodes.name: Friday, 19th November 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Will silent Sam help Lily when she starts to choke on a lolly? Angry David takes steps when he finds out about Max's cruelty.

episodes.name: Monday, 22nd November 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: The police discover the weapon that killed Natasha was used by Abi's criminal ex Tez. Will Roy crack when DS Abney asks more about the night of the sinkhole collapse?

episodes.name: Monday, 22nd November 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Kelly tells Stu about her part in Seb's fatal attack. Faye struggles with her return home as she's released from prison. Max faces the backlash about the film he made.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 24th November 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Nina fears Roy is going to take his own life when she finds out he's changed his will. Roy then admits he's leaving Weatherfield. Can Nina stop her uncle from going away?

episodes.name: Wednesday, 24th November 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Worried about Kelly, Imran dupes her flaky mum, Laura, into meeting him. Faye panics as she attempts to return to work at the Bistro. Will she fare better at the factory?

episodes.name: Friday, 26th November 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Homeless Kelly succumbs to taking drugs but will Nina come to her rescue when the out-of-it teen is cornered by a drunken mob? Kev whisks Abi away on honeymoon.

episodes.name: Friday, 26th November 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Angry Daniel finds out what Daisy has been up to on social media. Aggie accuses Grace of treating her like an unpaid babysitter. Ryan's on to shifty Zeedan.

episodes.name: Monday, 29th November 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Zeedan's dodgy money-laundering caper blows when Ryan finds out what's been going on and tells Alya. To Zee's horror, his sister confronts his blackmailer, Hashim.

episodes.name: Monday, 29th November 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Daisy and Daniel call time on their romance after a series of rows. When Curtis explains his family won't be at the wedding, Emma's on a mission to secretly bring them to the ceremony.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 1st December 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Curtis has a hospital appointment with his consultant. Later, he and Emma are stunned when his dad Neville turns up, but Curtis says he's his stepdad. Grace and Aggie clash.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 1st December 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Jenny urges Daisy to be honest with Daniel but she wants to move on with footballer Ashley. Zeedan books a pitch at the Christmas market to raise some capital.

episodes.name: Friday, 3rd December 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: When Zeedan's food truck vanishes, along with Hashim's dirty cash, Zeedan's ordered to torch the restaurant! As it goes up in flames, someone's inside... But who?

episodes.name: Friday, 3rd December 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Aggie confronts Grace about leaving baby Glory home alone and is appalled by her reaction. Fiz reels as she meets Phill's mum Mimi when he moves in for a few days.

episodes.name: Monday, 6th December 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Summer's crush on teacher Daniel is misinterpreted by jealous Max who accuses Daniel of abusing his position. As Summer puts Max in his place, all hell breaks loose.

episodes.name: Monday, 6th December 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Fiz continues to struggle with Phill's bossy mum, Mimi, and decides to tell her boyfriend about how she really feels, but how will Phill take Fiz's comments?

episodes.name: Wednesday, 8th December 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: When Fiz overhears Ty telling Mimi that Phill is the luckiest man alive, how will she react? A shocked Paul becomes convinced Daniel has been grooming Summer.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 8th December 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Things intensify following the insurance scam fire at Speed Daal as Kelly overhears a dodgy conversation between Elaine and Yasmeen. Could Stu have been involved?

episodes.name: Friday, 10th December 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: When Hashim collapses, clutching his chest, Zeedan takes the opportunity to pin the Speed Daal fire on his vicious father-in-law who's been blackmailing him for weeks.

episodes.name: Friday, 10th December 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Max faces permanent exclusion from school for the saga at the Ice Ball, which doesn't go down well with his furious dad, David. Sarah thinks she might be pregnant.

episodes.name: Monday, 13th December 2021
episodes.overview: Emma is thrown into a panic and rushes to A&E when Ruby accidentally swallows one of Curtis' heart pills..At school, Daniel avoids Summer and is thrown by a shock in class. Zeedan is redecorating Speed Daal when his estranged wife Marrium turns up. Fed up with Adam's reputation, Sarah demands to know how many women her hubby's slept with.

episodes.name: Tuesday, 14th December 2021
episodes.overview: Back at home, shell-shocked Emma assures Tyrone that Ruby is fine. But when Curtis comes home, making out he's tired after a run, Emma confronts him with his so-called pills and wants answers. Will Curtis finally open up and admit all? Billy takes Summer to the Bistro but will he notice the signs that her eating disorder has returned? Sarah invites her new pal Lydia for a drink. In the Rovers, Lydia clocks Adam and it's clear she knows him.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 15th December 2021
episodes.overview: Emma quizzes Dr Handley about Curtis' heart condition and when she gets nowhere, she calls his 'stepdad' Neville and asks about his illness. Sarah reels when Lydia reveals she's a got a past with Adam. But Adam plays it down. Maria informs horrified Sally that she's going to run for council.

episodes.name: Thursday, 16th December 2021
episodes.overview: Emma tells Curtis she can't trust him and demands he moves out. Before she's able to tell Steve, her dad heaps praise on poorly Curtis' fundraising. Sally is aghast when Maria trashes her reputation. Gail is relieved when she makes progress with Audrey, and Marrium thaws towards Zeedan.

episodes.name: Friday, 17th December 2021
episodes.overview: As Curtis insists he's in love with Emma, will she change her mind about the wedding? Steve gives Curtis his card and asks him to bank the new funds into Oliver's charity account. Yasmeen offers Stu a room but he puts his foot in it. Sarah suggests the Platts and Barlows unite for Christmas. Maria and Phill suspect foul play. Kev and Abi return from honeymoon.

episodes.name: Monday, 20th December 2021
episodes.overview: As bride Emma gets ready, she's still unsure. Steve tells Amy he gave Curtis his bank card, as Curtis looks into flights. Debbie wants Kev to warn Abi that Kelly is living at No.7 but he doesn't get the chance. It's crunch time for Max.

episodes.name: Monday, 20th December 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Kelly resolves to move away from the street to spare Abi's feelings. News of Max's fate comes through from his school. Lydia swiftly changes the subject when Sarah mentions Adam.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 22nd December 2021 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: At the concert Max tampers with Daniel's laptop. When he hears Daniel got him reinstated, can he undo his handiwork? Kev and Jack are thrilled when Abi gets festive. Kev then floored by a letter Ty found among Seb's things.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 22nd December 2021 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Daisy impresses Daniel with her passionate defence of his character. A furtive Kevin keeps a secret from Abi. Sarah begins to regret suggesting a joint family Christmas.

episodes.name: Friday, 24th December 2021
episodes.overview: Kevin pulls out all the stops to deliver a miracle for Abi... Nina turns down Asha's offer to spend Christmas with her. Daisy goes to a party with Ashley but leaves and comes looking for Daniel. Daniel meets Sarah's friend Lydia.

episodes.name: Saturday, 25th December 2021
episodes.overview: At No.9, Ty and Evelyn are interrupted by the arrival of Fiz and the girls! When Phill also turns up, will there be trouble? As Sarah despairs over her family's behaviour, can Adam save the day? Eileen's horrified by George's gift.

episodes.name: Sunday, 26th December 2021
episodes.overview: Dev is alarmed when Abi unnerves Kelly in the Bistro. Nick is happy when he hears silent Sam speaking to Hope. Nina confides her anxiety in Asha who comes up with i solution. Ellen finds out Gail was behind George's gift idea.

episodes.name: Monday, 27th December 2021
episodes.overview: .Abi slaps Imran when he tells her to leave Kelly alone. Kelly is sacked, and Craig then finds her out of it on Spice. Ty tells Evelyn he's waiting for Phill to get bored of playing stepdad. But Phill tells Fiz he's found them a family house.

episodes.name: Tuesday, 28th December 2021
episodes.overview: As Aadi lays into Dev for pushing Kelly away, Abi listens in. At a drugs support group Abi glares as Kelly talks. Evelyn insists it's Ty's duty to do right by Fiz and the kids Lydia's stung by Sarah's take on her past with Adam.

episodes.name: Friday, 31st December 2021
episodes.overview: Emma drops Tim at A&E and spots Curtis getting out of a cab! At a hotel, Sarah and Adam's evening is ruined. Will Jenny spend New Year's Eve alone... or with Leo? Kelly is thrilled when Maria offers her her job back.

episodes.name: Monday, 3rd January 2022 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Abi meets Imran to discuss her taking a pregnancy test and warns him she'll have to tell Kev if it's positive. Has someone overheard? Tim books health checks for him and Sally.

episodes.name: Monday, 3rd January 2022 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: As tipsy Emma supervises learner driver Faye when they return from a party, Faye clips an old man, Ted. They're relieved he seems OK and later return to check on him.

episodes.name: Tuesday, 4th January 2022
episodes.overview: When Adam's car is keyed, he accuses Lydia of doing it and trying to drive a wedge between him and Sarah. But Adam's left eating his words... can he rectify the issue? Worried Sally jumps to conclusions when she realises Tim's lying about what he's been up to. Zeedan tells Alya that Marrium will be returning to London very soon.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 5th January 2022 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Yasmeen and Stu ready to reopen Speed Daal. After sharing a kiss, Zeedan and Marrium agree to try again. Craig and Faye move in with Ty and Emma. Adam lands Lydia.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 5th January 2022 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Tim reels when his consultant informs him he needs a triple heart bypass. In the dark, Sally is wounded when he turns down her suggestion of sexy night in.

episodes.name: Monday, 10th January 2022 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Zeedan and Ryan find a use for Hashim's dirty cash. A miserable Joseph pleads poverty to Hope. Aggie forces Tim to fave up to his illness.

episodes.name: Monday, 10th January 2022 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Yasmeen is incensed by Alya and Zeedan's confession. Chesney and Gemma learn that Joseph is being bullied. Tim summons the courage to inform Sally of his upcoming operation.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 12 January 2022 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Joseph reacts badly when Chesney goes back on his word. Aadi encourages Amy to bury the hatchet with Summer. Jenny intervenes to ease Rita's burden.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 12 January 2022 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Chesney and Gemma report Joseph's disappearance to the police. Zeedan's must choose between his wife and family. Brian recruits Shona to assist Rita in The Kabin.

episodes.name: Friday, 14th January 2022
episodes.overview: Tim confides in Peter that he needs to have a triple-bypass operation. Will he take Peter's advice to tell his wife Sally? A cash reward is offered for Joseph's safe return. Summer's troubles continue when she discovers she's been upskirted. But the teen feels too ashamed to alert the police and instead comforts herself with chocolate.

episodes.name: Monday, 17th January 2022 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Tim's shady behaviour about his bypass operation has Sally convinced that her secretive husband is cheating on her!

episodes.name: Monday, 17th January 2022 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Amy is suspended for painting 'Stop Protecting Sex Offenders' on the school wall! At the corner shop, Bernie plants a kiss on Dev.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 19 January 2022 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Yasmeen struggles to rely on agency staff at Speed Daal, while Leanne offers Zeedan some work at the Bistro.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 19th January 2022 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: When Sally tracks Tim via a phone app, she discovers he's in hotel and vows to confront him. Will Tim admit the truth?

episodes.name: Friday, 21st January 2022
episodes.overview: Before Tim can break the news to Sally about his operation, he collapses, clutching his chest. Jenny has a date with Leo. Summer and Amy lead a protest against the upskirters, and Daniel secretly calls The Gazette to get the story covered.

episodes.name: Monday, 24th January 2022 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Bernie's chuffed when Dev suggests a meal in Speed Daal to make their romance official. Carla has words with Jenny about Leo.

episodes.name: Monday, 24th January 2022 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Tim's due to have surgery and wants Sally to forgive him before he goes under the knife but things take an unexpected turn.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 26th January 2022 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Guilty Faye and Emma panic when Craig shares an update on Ted's case. Lydia clocks a spark between exes Daniel and Daisy.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 26th January 2022 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Evelyn calls the police about Bernie. Will the gran admit the truth about the money? Jenny learns Leo's been taken to A&E.

episodes.name: Friday, 28th January 2022
episodes.overview: Faye's horrified when Emma suggests they attend Ted's funeral. Later, she crumbles and tells Craig about knocking Ted down. As the family turn their back on Bernie, will Joseph or Hope put everyone straight? Sally fumes as Elaine says she's moving in.

episodes.name: Monday, 31st January 2022 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Faye frets when Craig tells her that he's going to conduct an extra search of Ted's house. Will she get him to do her dirty work?

episodes.name: Monday, 31st January 2022 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Tyrone steals himself to tell Fiz there's more to Hope's problems than they fIrst thought, and It's time to get a proper diagnosis.

episodes.name: Tuesday, 1st February 2022
episodes.overview: When Daniel returns home to find Max destroying his flat, he shoves him and he falls down the stairs. Will the teen survive? Stressed about Faye's involvement in Ted's death and what it means for his career, Craig decides to quit the police force.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 2nd February 2022 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: The cops are on Daniel's back about Max, but Daniel maintains that the lad slipped. Daniel and Daisy share a kiss.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 2nd February 2022 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Asha's worried sick when a deeply troubled Nina steals her phone and locks her in the cafe to stop her leaving for Glasgow.

episodes.name: Monday, 7th February 2022 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Adam blames a client when his car window is smashed and his office i raided by armed police following tip-off about a gun.

episodes.name: Monday, 7th February 2022 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Laura announces she's dying from stomach cancer and has only months to live. But Kelly's unsure how to react to the news.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 9th February 2022 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Plagued by silent phone calls, Adam is determined to catch his tormentor, especially when Sarah receives flowers with a scary note.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 9th February 2022 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: On Amy's birthday, Steve and Tracy find an intruder in their home who they unmask as Jacob. But Jacob is Amy's secret boyfriend.

episodes.name: Friday, 11th February 2022
episodes.overview: When Summer and Asha work out Amy is dating Jacob, Amy begs them not to spill the beans to her dad Steve. Adam's stalker sneaks into his and Sarah's flat, trashes their roses and leaves a note saying this Valentine's Day might be their last.

episodes.name: Monday, 14th February 2022 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Amy collapses while clubbing, but all hell breaks loose at the hospital when Steve discovers Amy and Jacob are an item.

episodes.name: Monday, 14th February 2022 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: It's Valentine's Day and, as Sarah spends it alone, Lydia's behaviour towards Adam is like a scene out of "Fatal Attraction".

episodes.name: Wednesday, 16th February 2022 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Jacob tries to reassure Steve he didn't spike Amy's drink, but he ends up being punched by the dad and dumped by Amy.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 16th February 2022 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Joseph's nan Linda turns unannounced at No.5, leaving Chesney lying through his teeth that coping with five kids is easy.

episodes.name: Friday, 18th February 2022
episodes.overview: Max is forced to hand over the footage of the Valentine's dance to detectives investigating Amy's spiking. What will it show? Unaware who Linda is, Dev tells her about Joseph's recent ordeal. Abi squirms as Toyah tells her that Imran cheated.

episodes.name: Monday, 21st February 2022 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Linda starts to take a more active role in Joseph's life and ends up suggesting her grandson moves to Portugal to live with her.

episodes.name: Monday, 21st February 2022 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: As Toyah and Iran celebrate their engagement, Abi confesses to Sally that she cheated on Kev. Lydia spins Sarah a line.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 23rd February 2022 (Part 1)
episodes.overview: After Jack's adoption hearing, Sally phones Abi about her pal's secret betrayal unaware her call is going out over a speaker.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 23rd February 2022 (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Stu sets out to bring Tracy down a peg or two. Adam learns his reputation has been trashed online. Bernie and Linda clash.

episodes.name: Friday, 25th February 2022
episodes.overview: As Sarah pieces the 'facts' together, she accuses Lydia of having an affair with Adam. Adam reels as Lydia says it's true. Abi and Imran are on pins when Toyah catches them talking about their secret fling. Stu tells Ken that he pranked Tracy.

episodes.name: Monday, 28th February 2022
episodes.overview: Cheney agrees to let Linda take Joseph to Portugal, only for him to regret it, which results in a frantic dash to the airport. Emma spies on Ted's grandson, Jon, which leads to dinner at Speed Daal, but she's torn when Faye hears about it and kicks off.

episodes.name: Friday, 4th March 2022
episodes.overview: Lydia's out to destroy Adam's life by giving Sarah 'evidence' of her hubby's affair and making it look like Adam trashed her flat. As Abi continues to spiral downwards, she knocks back vodka and buys drugs while obsessing over photos of Seb.

episodes.name: Sunday, 6th March 2022
episodes.overview: Abi gets high with Dean and they take off in a stolen car, but when she doubles over in pain, he leaves her stranded. What's wrong?

episodes.name: Monday, 7th March 2022
episodes.overview: Kelly struggles with juggling more shifts at the salon and sneaking off to look after her terminally ill mum Laura. Nick worries when Sam's chess obsession affects his schoolwork. Tyrone discovers a car has been stolen and realises Abi is behind it.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 9th March 2022
episodes.overview: When Daniel's former love interest Nicky comes looking for him, an unnerved Daisy lies that he's moved away. Maria says Laura can move in with them, and Gary's horrified when Laura says she's hiring a detective to track down Rick.

episodes.name: Friday, 11th March 2022
episodes.overview: Daniel's delighted when Nicky tracks him down. But when he introduces her to Daisy, his other half has some explaining to do. Ed and Aggie are relieved when Michael calls off the search for Grace. Gary's on edge when he goes with Laura to meet her Pl.

episodes.name: Monday, 14th March 2022
episodes.overview: Abi admits the truth when Imran demands to know if he's the father of her baby, Alfie. just as Toyah walks in on them. Daisy learns Nicky's applying for a teaching-assistant job. Aggie and Ed worry when Grace turns up for Glory's birthday party.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 16th March 2022
episodes.overview: When Alfie has an operation, Abi breaks down to Kevin who's returned and gives her hope when he offers to let her stay at No.13. Ed and Aggie tell astounded Michael that Grace has been blackmailing them. Amy's bids to meet with Jacob are dashed.

episodes.name: Friday, 18th March 2022
episodes.overview: When Amy tells Steve and Tracy that she and Jacob are in love, Steve insists she chooses her family or her boyfriend! Carla tells Sarah to think hard before giving up on Adam because she's not sure Lydia can be trusted. What will Sarah do?

episodes.name: Monday, 21st March 2022
episodes.overview: Lydia's bombshell brings Adam crashing down to earth. Steve meddles to prevent Ken and Dev from helping Amy. Phill reveals his plan to enable Maria to win the election. Laura mixes alcohol with her medication.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 23rd March 2022
episodes.overview: Adam undergoes surgery to save his eyesight. Kelly cannot contain her fury at Laura's selfishness. Craig struggles to forgive Faye for ruining his career. Maria receives the news she has been waiting for.

episodes.name: Friday, 25th March 2022
episodes.overview: As Gary resolves to moves Rick's body, Laura demands the truth. Faye confides in Elaine that she might be pregnant. Tim wants to celebrate Sally's return by heading for the bedroom.

episodes.name: Monday, 28th March 2022
episodes.overview: Gary and Maria panic as the police conduct a new search for Rick's body. Phill and Fiz's house move suffers more than one setback. Tim blames his mum for his underwhelming performance. Emma fibs to Craig after getting caught out with Jon.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 30th March 2022
episodes.overview: Imran makes an impassioned plea for Abi to keep her baby. Tim fails to muster the courage to ask Elaine to move out. Maria is appalled by Gary's decision to confess to murder. Jon and Emma grow closer than ever.

episodes.name: Friday, 1st April 2022
episodes.overview: Kevin discovers a shocking secret from Alfie's birth certificate. Billy persuades Summer to join her friends for a girls' night out. Fiz and Phill are surprised by Tyrone's gesture. Nick confronts Leanne over Sam's clandestine chess matches.

episodes.name: Monday, 4th April 2022
episodes.overview: Jon offers Emma a new life in Australia. Toyah makes an important decision regarding Elsie's adoption. Tyrone wishes Fiz well for her fresh start in Phill's house. Roy encourages Nick to let Sam play in a chess tournament.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 6th April 2022
episodes.overview: Faye blurts out the truth when Jon demands answers. Gary is shocked by the decline in Laura's condition. Nick proudly watches Sam at the chess tournament. Tyrone admits to Fiz that he misses her.

episodes.name: Friday, 8th April 2022
episodes.overview: Kelly refuses to allow Laura to ruin her moment of glory. Sam faces his opponent in the chess final. Daisy suspects Nicky of being cagey about her past career. And will Emma get a happy ending as she leaves the street?

episodes.name: Monday, 11th April 2022
episodes.overview: While Kelly grieves for her mum, news arrives concerning her dad. Toyah's heart breaks as Elsie is taken away from her. Sam seeks Nick's advice on the opposite sex. Nicky offers to help when Daniel agrees to organise a school trip.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 13th April 2022
episodes.overview: Imran decides to challenge Abi for custody of Alfie. Beth betrays Craig's confidence to a shocked Faye. Gary questions Maria's priorities. Mrs. Crawshaw puts Daniel in an awkward situation. A worried Billy persuades Amy to speak to Summer.

episodes.name: Friday, 15th April 2022
episodes.overview: Abi and Imran prepare to do battle for care of Alfie. Gary hopes to bury the past at Rick's funeral. Amy stumbles on Summer's secret. Kirk amazes his employers by winning a big order.

episodes.name: Monday, 18th April 2022
episodes.overview: Simon's vendetta against Jacob places Summer in harm's way. Toyah disapproves of Imran's sneaky tactics to beat Abi. Gary, Ed and Paul discover a stash of cash at Rick's house. A paranoid Daisy resolves to get Nicky away from Daniel.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 20th  April 2022
episodes.overview: Daisy learns the truth after trying to matchmake for Nicky. Sally instructs a reluctant Tim to send Elaine packing. Summer is upset by Todd's idea of looking out for her. Eileen feels stung by George's rejection.

episodes.name: Friday, 22nd April 2022
episodes.overview: Nicky gets summoned to a meeting at the school. Sean fuels Eileen's growing suspicions of George. Elaine's departure fails to solve Tim and Sally's problem. Summer meets a kindred spirit at her diabetes support group.

episodes.name: Monday, 25th April 2022
episodes.overview: Daniel apologises to an unforgiving Daisy, and reveals that it was Max who maliciously shared Nicky's images with the rest of the school. George refuses to let Eileen stay at his, and is shocked when he arrives home to find Eileen and Sean snooping round his garden.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 27th April 2022

Craig urges Faye to follow her heart, Evelyn badgers Roy to see about his chest pains and George accuses Brian of naval sabotage.

Roy is brought up short with chest pains during a dog walk, prompting Evelyn to call an ambulance. Sally suggests Craig and Tim should find a common hobby and Isabella gets bad news.

episodes.overview: As a new day dawns in Weatherfield, Stephen plans his escape from the cobbles and the trail of dead bodies, unaware that the residents of Coronation Street are putting together the pieces of a rather shocking jigsaw puzzle. Tim is distracted from Sally's plans for their wedding anniversary when a passing mention from Brian of Stephen's interest in the canal dredging project gets the cogs whirring.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 11th October 2023
episodes.overview: Sally starts to panic when Kevin tells her that Tim did not go to the match with him and Kirk, while a calm and collected Stephen tricks an oblivious Michael into enabling him to transfer the full balance of Underworld's account into a bogus one he has set up. The Platt family are stunned when Sarah breaks the news of Stephen defrauding Audrey and drugging Carla.

episodes.name: Friday, 13th October 2023

episodes.name: Friday, 9th August 2024
episodes.overview: Cassie kidnaps Alina to contrive a meeting with Tyrone, Rowan bestows extra responsibility on Leanne, and Mason is annoyed at Betsy for stirring up trouble with Dylan.

episodes.name: Monday, 12th August 2024
episodes.overview: Leanne keeps her distance as Toyah undergoes an operation, Kit moves into the Rovers, Steve misleads Cassie with an invitation to an evening of culture, and Aadi cautions Amy against investing her inheritance from Deirdre in the Institute.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 14th August 2024
episodes.overview: Nick declares his love for Toyah while Rowan applies more pressure, and Kit panics when Paul struggles to breathe. Steve's constant jibes tempt Cassie to quit working for Ken, and Joel fumbles an excuse when Dee-Dee learns that he booked a flight to Belfast.

episodes.name: Friday, 16th August 2024
episodes.overview: Joel's ex, Emily, sets alarm bells ringing for Dee-Dee, and Mason encourages Betsy to report the man behind her bruises. Tracy is unimpressed to find Cassie caring for Ken, and Ryan and Kit discuss their love of vinyl records over a drink.

episodes.name: Monday, 19th August 2024
episodes.overview: The pieces fall into place for Dee-Dee as Joel's deceit becomes clear, Toyah discovers Nick has blabbed to David, Cassie reckons Tracy is lying about her idyllic life in Spain, and Tyrone accuses Hope of tormenting Alina with anonymous calls.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 21st August 2024
episodes.overview: Dee-Dee is stunned by Joel's audacity as she demands the truth, Beth goes for a job interview, Tyrone comes clean to Fiz about his legal consultation, and Toyah hopes for good news from the hospital.

episodes.name: Friday, 23rd August 2024
episodes.overview: Alina's fear that she is being watched proves to be justified, and Sarah faces another grilling from Lisa. Dee-Dee braces herself for a difficult conversation with Emily, Daniel confides in Daisy that he does not trust Kit, and Amy's decision to quit her job at the bistro delights Rowan

episodes.name: Monday, 26th August 2024
episodes.overview: Leanne is unnerved to notice Rowan recording Amy's upload session, Beth spots Kit in an incriminating situation, and Betsy persuades Mason to skive off work to be with her.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 28th August 2024
episodes.overview: Amy flees in distress when Leanne pushes her too far, Betsy dumps Mason, and Adam cajoles Dee-Dee back to work. Kit threatens to end Craig's career unless Beth leaves town, and Tracy and Nick angrily confront Rowan.

episodes.name: Friday, 30th August 2024
episodes.overview: Lisa's boss delivers an update on the case against Joel, Betsy plants a stolen purse on Mason, and Jack frets as his court date approaches. Meanwhile, Craig quizzes Sid about his dealings with Beth, and Rowan gives Leanne an order regarding Amy.

episodes.name: Monday, 2nd September 2024
episodes.overview: Dee-Dee digs for dirt on Joel with his former employer, a nervous Jack appears in court, Betsy puts Dylan in the friend-zone, the quads have their first day at school, and Stefan's wife Coral introduces herself to Abi.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 4th September 2024
episodes.overview: Amy receives a frightening message, Lisa quizzes Kit about the evidence planted on Nathan, Summer comes to Paul's aid, Leanne goes through the files on Rowan's laptop, and Jack is sentenced for the arson attack on Stefan's property.

episodes.name: Friday, 6th September 2024
episodes.overview: Leanne summons Nick to the bistro, Paul encourages Billy to have fun with David, and Carla provokes Joel in front of a client. Ken admits that although physically he no longer needs Cassie's help, he enjoys her company and would like her to stay on, while Tracy accuses the ex-addict of trying to get her claws into Steve.

episodes.name: Monday, 9th September 2024
episodes.overview: Billy is thrown into a panic when he loses his phone, which contain all his previous photos and memories. But as he retraces his steps, Summer and Bernie are horrified to find Paul struggling to breathe on the sofa. Can Billy get back home in time? Nick reports Rowan to the police, while Leanne tells Amy she may have the evidence to recover her money.

episodes.name: Friday, 13th September 2024
episodes.overview: Billy is hit with the sad reality of life without Paul, while tensions are high within his family as they grieve. Can they pull together to plan his funeral? Ruby and Dorin go missing while in Tyrone's care, Lisa seeks Craig's help in tracing one of Joel's victims and Nick delivers news concerning Rowan.

episodes.name: Monday, 16th September 2024
episodes.overview: Lauren receives a visitor with the power to end Joel's reign of terror, Tyrone stops Alina and Dorin catching a plane, Debbie offers Bethany a job, and Tracy advises Steve to pursue Cassie.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 18th September 2024
episodes.overview: Lisa and Dee-Dee trace the source of the drugs Joel fed to Lauren, Alina learns of Tyrone's devious tactics, Bernie and Billy have differing ideas for Paul's funeral, and Daisy agrees to mind Bertie for Daniel.

episodes.name: Friday, 20th September 2024
episodes.overview: Betsy makes a guilty confession to Carla and Lisa, Ryan confronts Daisy over her feelings for Daniel, and Lauren discovers she is under investigation for trying to abort her baby.

episodes.name: Monday, 23rd September 2024
episodes.overview: Word reaches Daniel and Sarah that Bethany is in intensive care in Turkey, Ronnie and Ed step in to protect Dee-Dee from Joel, and Gemma suggests a compromise to Bernie

episodes.name: Wednesday, 25th September 2024
episodes.overview: Daniel learns that Bethany's travel insurance does not cover her medical bills, Gary sees red when Mason is released, Lauren confides Joel's movements to Dee-Dee, and Fiz celebrates her 40th birthday.

episodes.name: Friday, 27th September 2024
episodes.overview: Daniel decides to crowd-fund for Bethany's medical costs, Mason arrives at work sporting a black eye, and a drunken Joel corners Roy in the cafe.

episodes.name: Monday, 30th September 2024
episodes.overview: The police find evidence indicating that Joel has taken his own life, Fiz has an appointment with the doctor, Stu discovers Mason has spent the night in the restaurant, and Adam gets a shock while checking Sarah's voicemails.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 2nd October 2024
episodes.overview: Billy encounters an unwelcome mourner at the church for Paul's funeral, Sarah is unimpressed by the cosmetic surgery clinic's financial offer, and Tyrone and Fiz are stunned when Hope defiantly admits to stealing a vape from the corner shop.

episodes.name: Friday, 4th October 2024
episodes.overview: Bernie collects Paul's ashes ahead of the rave in his memory, Gail suggests selling her house to pay Bethany's medical bills, Carla receives a letter that upsets her, and Dee-Dee confronts Joel's dad.

episodes.name: Monday, 7th October 2024
episodes.overview: Carla attends court, where she comes face to face with her victim's father, Tom - and back at the factory she takes her anger out on Betsy and Sally. Billy reads out Paul's wish list for his loved ones, David tells Shona that Gail has taken out a loan meaning she is now committed to selling the house, and Kit is horrified by what he finds on Joel's laptop.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 9th October 2024
episodes.overview: Bethany returns from Turkey and is taken straight to hospital, where Sarah tells a guilt-ridden Daniel he is not welcome. Carla tells Lisa they need to talk and Eileen does not agree with Stu and Yasmeen giving Mason a chance. Gemma is touched when Chesney orders her to take the day off and put her feet up. Cassie makes Hope and Ruby promise to pull together for Fiz's sake.

episodes.name: Friday, 11th October 2024
episodes.overview: The Platts are baffled by Jesse's arrival, so Shona urges Sarah and David to talk to him. Stu and Yasmeen receive a brick through their window. Adam confesses to Sarah that Damon offered to pay Bethany's medical bills. Hope's vaping habit ignites danger.

episodes.name: Monday, 14th October 2024
episodes.overview: As Craig and Kit investigate Joel's whereabouts, three lads find a body floating in a nearby river. Daisy hears that Bethany has dumped Daniel, so she heads to the hospital to put her straight. Stu is angry with Yasmeen when the social worker finds him somewhere to live, so he makes a momentous decision.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 16th October 2024
episodes.overview: Lisa discovers that Joel died after being struck across the head by a heavy weapon, so she is interested to learn that Yasmeen threw Mason out because he had a crowbar. David works out how to buy the house and is guarded when Jesse offers to help out. Gemma tells Chesney she doesn't want Joseph to go on the school skiing trip, fearing for his safety after losing Paul.

episodes.name: Friday, 18th October 2024
episodes.overview: Ronnie rumbles Debbie's plan for a surprise party to mark his 55th birthday - but his good mood falters when Kit arrives to question him and Ed. Jesse treats David, Sarah and Nick to lunch in the Rovers, where they quiz him on is finances. Nick asks Lauren how she found sleeping on the sofa of No 8 the other week and Jenny suggests to Chesney that Gemma might like to come back to work.

episodes.name: Monday, 21st October 2024
episodes.overview: Bethany encounters a masked intruder upon her return home from hospital, Dee-Dee is overwhelmed during a meeting with Lauren's social worker, Nick and Leanne divide up their belongings, and Kit reckons Gemma has returned to work too soon.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 23rd October 2024
episodes.overview: An ambulance is called for Gail following a family row, and Chesney leaves Kirk in charge while he dashes to the airport. Kit finds Dee-Dee's behaviour suspicious, Max admits his feelings for Lauren, and Jesse fishes for a confession from David.

episodes.name: Sunday, 27th October 2024
episodes.overview: Jesse questions David's guilt over Gail's condition, Toyah makes amends to Sam, and Bethany flips when Daniel sees her stoma bag. Elsewhere, Damon informs Sarah that her family is in the clear, and Cassie shows off her new holiday outfit to Steve.

episodes.name: Monday, 28th October 2024
episodes.overview: Lisa follows up an unexpected lead on Joel's murder, Jesse's announcement stuns the Platts, Dev refuses to pay Chesney's wages, Nick asks Toyah to be his manager, and Steve boosts Cassie's self-esteem after a bad date.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 30th October 2024
episodes.overview: Betsy jumps to conclusions upon catching sight of Lisa's bruises, Aadi advises Dev to make a romantic gesture to Bernie, Adam voices concern about Ken's spending, Kit uses insider info to impress Daisy, and Ryan queries Carla's movements on the night of Joel's murder.

episodes.name: Friday, 1st November 2024
episodes.overview: Lisa points the finger when a formal complaint is made against her, Dev witnesses an intense exchange between Mason and Liam, Ryan rumbles Kit's duplicity, and Billy learns of Bernie's intention to hold a screening party for Paul's ashes launch.

episodes.name: Monday, 4th November 2024
episodes.overview: Daisy tackles Kit about stolen whisky, Tim and Sally suspect they have a mouse at number four, and Daniel reveals Bethany's struggles to her nurse. Summer arrives home to find a stranger waiting in the flat, and Lisa gives an account of her whereabouts when Joel was killed.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 6th November 2024
episodes.overview: An emotional Billy chooses the worst moment to confess his sins, Bethany suffers a humiliation after venturing out of the flat, Dee-Dee keeps her distance from Lauren, Tim catches Mason red-handed, and David hides a secret from Shona.

episodes.name: Friday, 8th November 2024
episodes.overview: Bernie finds a frozen and barely conscious Billy, Tim helps Mason to look for a place to spend the night, and Dee-Dee decides to hand herself in to the police.

episodes.name: Monday, 11th November 2024
episodes.overview: Dee-Dee approaches Kit and admits to hitting Joel with a crowbar, Tim confronts Mason and his brothers, Gemma refuses to forgive Billy, and David pays Clayton a visit in prison.

episodes.name: Wednesday, 13th November 2024
episodes.overview: Lisa tells Carla that she suspects Joel's murderer is trying to frame her, Mason's tip-off enables Sally and Tim to recover their stolen car, and Shona is upset to learn that Clayton is in hospital.

episodes.name: Friday, 15th November 2024
episodes.overview: While Kit interviews his chief suspect, the true events of the night of Joel Deering's murder are finally revealed, but who did kill the psycho solicitor?
